sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant NM as NodeManager
    participant LCE as LinuxContainerExecutor
    participant Docker as Docker Daemon
    participant Container as Docker Container
    
    NM->>LCE: Launch Container (Execute container-executor)
    LCE->>Docker: REST: POST /containers/create
    Docker-->>LCE: Container ID
    LCE->>Docker: REST: POST /containers/start
    Docker->>Container: Spawn CMD (e.g. process.py)
    activate Container
    Container-->>Docker: Heartbeat/Logs
    Container-->>NM: Local stats (via host mount /proc)
    Container->>Container: Complete calculations
    Container-->>Docker: Exit status 0
    deactivate Container
    Docker-->>LCE: Container Stopped (Exit Code 0)
    LCE-->>NM: Report Container Completed (Exit Code 0)
